    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_45339E90-22D1-0135-C888-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Settings, instructors can hide total grades from students. By default, assignment group totals are visible to students when they <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-view-my-grades-in-a-current-course/ta-p/493" target="_blank">view their course grades</a>. For courses using weighted assignment groups, assignment group totals are always hidden from students.</p>
<p>If your course is using <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-use-grading-periods-in-a-course/ta-p/1030" target="_blank">Multiple Grading Periods</a>, this setting restricts students from viewing grades in any grading period.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_settings" data-step-uuid="D8686E27-3F57-47CF-8DC7-50C8365B52AE">
    <h2 id="open_settings" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Settings</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/755/119/original/b99d1318-82a6-4743-a65a-935ff32c4f76.png" srcset="" alt="Open Settings" height="275" width="158">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_45357940-22D1-0135-C88A-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_course_details" data-step-uuid="3377eab1-ed1f-49a7-afd9-39ca8202aacb">
    <h2 id="open_course_details" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Course Details</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/176/139/original/838f73e1-12b3-4572-9166-ec879236ee07.png" srcset="" alt="Open Course Details" height="82" width="670">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_4535A900-22D1-0135-C88C-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Course Details</strong> tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="hide_totals_in_student_grades_summary" data-step-uuid="0E222533-023A-461D-B96F-795FEDB92B42">
    <h2 id="hide_totals_in_student_grades_summary" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Hide Totals in Student Grades Summary</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/239/981/original/b42144a3-0522-4e42-bd6a-96e5db2cf758.png" srcset="" alt="Hide Totals in Student Grades Summary" height="193" width="365">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_45360A30-22D1-0135-C890-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the <strong>Hide totals in student grades summary </strong>option.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="update_course_details" data-step-uuid="336E0E49-8020-4409-AEEF-D8017C40063A">
    <h2 id="update_course_details" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Update Course Details</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/791/850/original/d1e9dcc1-0495-4486-a577-df44e83c47d1.png" srcset="" alt="Update Course Details" height="65" width="211">
