      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_a14ded57-e210-407a-a310-f6b9e645a7f4" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When students <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-view-my-grades-in-a-current-course/ta-p/493" target="_blank">view their course grades</a>, an informational message indicates that the calculation of totals has been disabled. Assignment group names are displayed, but totals are hidden.</p>
